article_title: Senator doesn't see Medicaid expansion in Mo. this year
article_text:
By Paul Hackbarth

Posted Apr 27, 2015 at 10:00 AM

Updated Apr 27, 2015 at 10:08 AM

article_metadata.description: With Missouri's legislative session ending May 15, a state senator from Rolla says he doesn't see Medicaid expansion occurring in the state this year.
article_metadata.author: Paul Hackbarth
